CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 16, reads: "4. Pet Milk's home economist, Mrs. Louise R. Prothro, demonstrates food products on the Pittsburgh home Service Fair stage. This is Mrs. Prothro's third year as The Courier's demonstrator"
TitMainTitle: Louise R. Prothro and Eunice Brown performing cooking demonstration in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
